{"type": "article", "id": 34719, "title": "经常搬家？有这套模块化家具就行了｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-11-21T23:02:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 35066, "name": "Caserne"}, {"id": 7058, "name": "造作"}, {"id": 8928, "name": "Luca Nichetto"}, {"id": 35057, "name": "Elena Bompani"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 130, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161121174740aeJqbskPzxU784Mv.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Lathe Stool by Luca Nichetto</h3><p>为了提高空间利用率，不少设计师从小件家具入手尝试了各种改造。意大利设计师 Luca Nichetto 最近为<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">造作</a>设计了一张自带收纳功能的旋木小凳，圆润而小巧的造型能很好地融入到各种环境当中，承担起不同房间内置物的需要。只要转动凳面，就能沿着螺杆顺畅地将它旋转上升，采用静音设计的结构保证这一过程不会产生噪音。这是它的<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/item/300164\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 1988 元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173109Xr8pfPQ96F0eS14J.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173109Qn1btWmqJgGfxLUK.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173109423kLwYBSa1tOi8q.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173111nGVpaFvbEdQACUJO.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Vulcan by KitchBot</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>在高级餐厅中，有一种名为 Sous-Vide 的料理方法，指的是在真空状态下通过精准的温度控制对食物进行长时间的隔水加热。为了让人们能在家中重现这种真空低温的烹调方式，台湾设计团队 KitchBot 决定通过科技的力量让烹饪的时间和温度更便于控制，打造了这款名为 Vulcan 的智能温控插座。只要在电锅中放入配套的测温线，把电锅的电源插到这个插座中，通过应用选择相应的食谱之后，手机就会在温度达标时发出通知。有了精准的测量工具和食谱的帮助，熟悉的厨具也能带给人们全新的料理口感。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/vulcan\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为新台币 3600 元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173123jHlgmW6z2x4YfnPw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611211731232CSeTQF8tm7ykvjf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173123jD9LKzeEHuI5xVXf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>2017 year planner by Kelly Angood</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>你在意过贴在水果上的小标签吗？来自英国的 Kelly Angood 有收藏水果标签的习惯，还为此开通了一个 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/fruit_stickers/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> 账号，两年来每天都会进行更新。为了让标签收藏家能够更好地展示自己的收藏，Angood 设计了一款特殊的日历。365 天依照工作日和周末被设计成了虚线和实线的椭圆，将每天收集到的标签贴在上面，就成了一种独特的记录时间的方式。它既是一件独一无二的装饰，也是一个督促你每天食用水果的提醒。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/kellyangood/fruit-stickers-2017-year-planner\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 15 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173140Mpm6htb2OwcVEdnx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173140G5s9fnqy71YPIBm3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173140IReQs9nASawXbPNE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Sparkr by Power Practial</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"https://powerpractical.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Power Practial</a> 是一个来自美国的设计团队，他们曾在 Kickstarter 上成功发布了六个产品，最近他们又推出了一个多功能的日用工具 Sparkr。Sparkr 的外形类似常见的手电筒，一端可以提供照明，并且附带一个透明的盖子，挂在电筒上就能转变为灯笼，可以通过挂绳悬挂起来提供更均匀的照明效果。位于手柄的另一端的是带有防水功能的电动等离子打火机，为了防止不必要的点火，它还设计有安全装置，使用前需要连续按下三次按钮。在设计过程中，团队意识到他们还能将相似功能结合在一个更小的产品中，因此还设计了打火机造型的 Sparkr 迷你版。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/powerpractical/sparkr-and-sparkr-mini\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 35 美元，迷你版为 20 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173155NkSbIUO5qa74oBsK.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.697059\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173155e71oE5UabdjAHJZ0.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173154zjxpKsQaUXnf2qIO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.405882\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173154OumteidpfRsoBFLa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.163235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173154R3A9I6V1uzsHvNX8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173155iyQZpVPKMrGUF48z.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667647\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Itaca furniture by Elena Bompani</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>作为自己的硕士毕业设计，来自意大利的 <a href=\"http://elenabompani.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Elena Bompani</a> 为时不时需要搬家的租客和旅行者设计了一款相当灵活的模块化家具系统 Itaca，希望减轻搬家时需要处理各种家具的负担。这套系统由一系列轻量的木制组件和各种功能性的口袋、盒子和搁架构成，零部件之间则通过皮革带固定在一起，组装和拆卸起来都相当方便。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173223ShRo02zQsFgW1iGZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173220CnO9XJGB26wD4rPi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173221PiQgncUDSZeC2Tpt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173222lVphWbr2uw4XqACZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500423\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173222G6UuirEL5FZV4oNh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121173221tBE2F7JqzbhUODyQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Meraki by Caserne</h3><p>专门经营希腊进口食品的品牌 Meraki 最近委托加拿大设计工作室 <a href=\"http://studiocaserne.ca/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Caserne</a> 为其设计了包装和品牌形象。蓝白两色和像是小窗户一样的图案结合在一起，让顾客很容易就联想到希腊的海滨，简洁又不失特色，配合透明玻璃瓶身给人一种非常清爽的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121222001ProuMNg9G5CUWzTs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.730469\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121222003rO9AYFfBk1s2Ty4w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121222003MB59ANLacdORSVyT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121222002WxvhbAuYZQjN8F5B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121222001lMbE3m1TJhDGStnQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161121222001ErzdBIZGclJasXQm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}